'''palaeontography'''
#The [[representation]] of the [[form]]s of [[life]] existing in [[prehistoric]] or [[geologic]] times, especially as represented by [[fossil]]s.

===Etymology===
Greek ''palaios'' meaning old + Greek ''ōn'', ''ont'' meaning to be + Greek ''graphiā'' meaning the representation of.

